| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3288 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7dc92ce9-8ea1-55b8-962e-9fe9fd8dbdd9"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
